{
  "id": "adv_card_rio_05_02",
  "title": "神崎莉央 2話 貴方を知りたくて",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "ここが……麻奈がデビュー前に歌った場所……\n舞台のかわりになりそうなもの、本当に何もないのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is… the place where Mana sang before her debut…\nThere's really nothing here that looks like a stage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "突発的でしたからね。元々はチラシを配るだけの\nつもりだったんですけど、全然受け取ってもらえなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was quite spontaneous. Originally‚ I just planned to hand out flyers‚\nbut no one was taking them at all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "それで、その場の思い付きで歌ったってわけ？\n凄い行動力ね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ you ended up let her sing on the spot as an idea in the moment?\nQuite the act of spontaneity.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "後で、三枝さんに叱られましたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I got scolded by Saegusa-san later.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、それはそうでしょ\n今の貴方なら絶対やらないでしょうね、そんな無茶",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ well‚ that's understandable.\nYou wouldn't do something that reckless now‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "あの頃は、まだ若かったですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was younger back then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "今でも若いでしょ。馬鹿ね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're still young now. You're being silly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "……けど、当時の貴方の無茶がなければ\n麻奈は埋もれてしまっていたかもしれないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…But without your recklessness back then‚\nMana might have been buried in obscurity.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "レイーズの時も、二人で強行したんでしょう？\nおかげで、私達はあの子の引き立て役になったんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You forced your way through with Reyes too‚ right?\nThanks to that‚ we became her support act.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "あ、いえ、その節はいろいろと……\nその、俺も必死で……なんだかすみません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ no‚ that time was quite…\nWell‚ I did my best and… I'm sorry for causing trouble.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、いいのよ。仕事なんだから必死になって当然よ\n普通、そこまでするマネージャーはいないけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha‚ it's fine. It's only natural to be desperate for work.\nMost managers wouldn't go that far.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "……ねえ、もし、私が貴方の初めての\n担当アイドルだったとしたら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hey‚ what if I were your first\nidol to manage?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "私のこと、同じくらい必死になってくれた？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Would you have been just as desperate for me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "え？　それは……もちろんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Well… of course.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、貴方なら、絶対にそう言うわよね\nそういうことにしておきましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ I knew you'd say that for sure.\nLet's just leave it at that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "聞いても仕方ないこと、聞いちゃったわね\n……あの子には、もう、どうやっても勝てないんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's no use asking about things like that.\n…Well‚ there's no way I could ever beat her now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "何か言いましたか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did you say something just now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "なんでもないわ。そろそろ、次の場所に行きましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ it's nothing. Let's go to the next location soon.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 106.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "映像では見たことあるけど……\n本当に小さなステージね。私達には縁がなかったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've seen it in videos before‚ but…\nSuch a small stage. We never had any connection to it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "はは、当時のLizNoirは東京を中心に\n活動してましたからね。無理もありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha‚ back then LizNoir was mainly active\nin Tokyo. It's understandable.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "ここで、麻奈は正式にデビューしたのね\n凄い人出だったんでしょう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ this is where Mana officially debuted?\nIt must have been a huge crowd‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "はい、俺も嬉しかったです。もしガラガラだったら\nどうしようって、前日は眠れませんでしたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I was happy too. I couldn't sleep the night before‚\nthinking about what if there were only a few people.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 135.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "貴方の心配性はその頃からだったのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You've always been a worrier‚ huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 139.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02-rio016.m4a",
      "text": "デビューライブで、お客さんがまばらなんて\nよくある話よ。特別めずらしくもないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Having a sparse audience for a debut live is common.\nIt's not that unusual.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。それでも俺は、麻奈の歌を聴いてほしくて\nだから前日の夜も、駅前でチラシを配ったりしてました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right. Even so‚ I wanted people to hear Mana's song.\nSo‚ the night before‚ I was handing out flyers in front of the station.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 154.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02-rio017.m4a",
      "text": "……あのねぇ、そんなことして当日体を壊したら\n周囲に迷惑が掛かるのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Listen‚ doing things like that and then getting sick on the actual day‚\nit inconveniences those around you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 161.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02-rio018.m4a",
      "text": "前から言おうと思ってたんだけど、貴方、働き過ぎよ\n少しは自分の体を大事にしなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've been meaning to say this for a while‚ but you tend to overwork yourself.\nTaking care of your own body is important too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 168.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02-rio019.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈は確かに特別だった。だからそうまでして\n人を集めたかった気持ちは、分からないでもないけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mana was indeed special. So I can understand to some extent\nthe feeling of wanting to gather people like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "それは違います。麻奈だけじゃない。必要があれば\n莉央さんのためにだって、どんな無茶でもやりますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not just about Mana. If it's necessary‚\nI'd go to any lengths‚ even for your sake‚ Rio-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02-rio020.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうなの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-Is that so?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 184.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 186.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02-rio021.m4a",
      "text": "……こほん。でも今後、私達のライブ前にそんな無理を\nして、倒れてでもしてみなさい。絶対に許さないわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ahem. But from now on‚ if you ever push yourself so hard\nbefore our live shows‚ to the point of collapsing even‚ I won't forgive you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 191.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 195.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "うっ……肝に銘じておきます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… I'll keep that in mind.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 195.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 198.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02-rio022.m4a",
      "text": "当時の貴方に言ってやりたいわ\n少しは自分のことも考えろって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'd like to tell that to the you back then.\nAt least think about yourself a little.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 201.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02-rio023.m4a",
      "text": "……でも、当時から熱意は全然変わっていないのね\nそこだけは、褒めてあげてもいいわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…But your enthusiasm hasn't changed at all since then.\nI suppose I can give credit for that much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 209.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 211.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "あ、ありがとうございます。\nなのに麻奈ときたら、やたら注文が多いんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Th-Thank you.\nAnd yet‚ with Mana‚ she's always so demanding.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 214.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "もっと音は大きくだとか、お客さんの顔が見たいとか\n……まったく",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Saying the sound needs to be louder‚ or she wants to see the audience's faces more…\n…Honestly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 224.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 226.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02-rio024.m4a",
      "text": "随分、嬉しそうに話すのね。やっぱりにやけてるわ\nもしかして、私、のろけられてる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You seem so happy talking about it. Are you glowing?\nCould it be‚ are you bragging about me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 231.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そんなことありませんよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Th-That's not it at all!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 234.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 237.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
