      "text": "はぁ……。まぁいいわ。最後に\nもう一つ行ってみたい場所があるんだけど、いい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sigh… Well‚ whatever. Last thing.\nThere's one more place I'd like to go.",
        "id": ""
