      "startTime": 269.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 273.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02-rio029.m4a",
      "text": "仕事だけじゃなく、学校でもべったりだったのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not just at work‚ you were quite attached in school too‚ weren't you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 273.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "べったりなんかはしてませんよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wasn't attached like that at all!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 277.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 279.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02-rio030.m4a",
      "text": "はいはい、べったりしてないべったりしてない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ yes‚ you weren't attached‚ you weren't attached.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 279.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02-koh018.m4a",
      "text": "さっきからなんなんです？　莉央さん、変ですよ\nいつもの仕事モードの莉央さんと全然違う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What's going on since earlier? Rio-san‚ you're acting strange.\nThis is completely different from the usual work mode Rio-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 286.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 289.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02-rio031.m4a",
      "text": "それはそうよ。だって今日は仕事じゃなくて\n個人的興味で来たんだから",
      "translations": {
